    <div data-cid="2028479">
        <div class="main review-item" id="2028479">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xiaojia86/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img2.doubanio.com/icon/u1387717-143.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xiaojia86/" class="name">肖浑</a>

            <span class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>

        <span content="2009-05-17" class="main-meta">2009-05-17 12:38:37</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://movie.douban.com/review/2028479/">繁华落尽，真纯尽显</a></h2>

                <div id="review_2028479_short" class="review-short" data-rid="2028479">
                    <div class="short-content">

                            这些年来，胖子王晶在电影圈一直处于游离状态，不再如十年前那么呼风唤雨了。现如今，所有的香港导演都在往内地发展，几乎非合拍片不拍，为了符合合拍片的条件，女主角都是内地女演员，于是出现了吴君如的怨言。而王晶，他的电影曾经具备了港片的诸多特点：咸湿、搞笑、奇...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2028479-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
